defaultThe plans will also align accountability with those who bear risk, whilst as set out above, also provide protections for all north of England interests.  
defaultThe overall decision-making structures will be capable of t
defaultaking financial responsibilities and have a substantial capacity to manage and bear risk.  Within the proposed structure larger authorities, or groupings of smaller authorities, have the choice of taking on franchise-wide risks
